					<div class="comment-metadata">
						<a href="https://thebluepaper.com/protecting-sexual-predators/#comment-3743"><time datetime="2015-06-22T09:55:30-04:00">June 22, 2015 at 9:55 am</time></a>					</div><!-- .comment-metadata -->

